the application this matter arises from strike action taken by employees of several contractors on 5, 6, 8, 24 and 25 june 2009 at a high rise building site at 915 hay street, perth ("site") which is controlled by diploma constructions (wa) pty ltd. in its substantive application filed in june 2009, the applicant ("the abcc") seeks relief in respect of alleged breaches by the respondents of s 38 of the building and construction industry improvement act 2005 (cth) (bcii act ), a civil penalty provision, which prohibits a person engaging in unlawful industrial action.
